
Basic Build
------------------

It can be built with pure make (last resort), cmake, or meson (preferable)

1) make
make
# make install

2) cmake
cmake -B _build -S $(pwd)
cmake --build _build
# cmake --install _build

3) meson
meson setup _build
meson compile -C _build
# meson install -C _build


Package Templates
------------------

Template samples are located in
debian/
rpmlinux/
archlinux/
snap/

